## 1. Product Overview

**ICP Hunter** is a self-service SaaS tool to help users identify their Ideal Customer Profiles (ICPs) on Twitter/X.

**Pay-per-use** with no subscriptions or long-term commitment.

**Positioning:**

ğŸ¯ "Letâ€™s hunt your perfect customers, one analysis at a time â€“ no subscriptions, just results."

**Brand personality:**

Playful but professional â€“ Looney Tunes-inspired meets startup energy.

Aligned with @theunderdoglabs on Twitter.

**Language & metaphor:**

